name: ✴ 𝕯𝖊𝖆𝖉 𝕯𝖗𝖊𝖆𝖒 ✴
description:
✴ Portrait of Dead Dream

A portrait of one's dead dream. It's universal and commonly found in space. It's shattered, but not exactly dead. It can be revived with the right star.

✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consisting of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
